Your all thinking of the friendly neighborhood fat guy driving around in the Parmalat trucks, but no, that's not the idea. When you think &quot;Milk man&quot; think &quot;Water man&quot; (or whatever that guy in the spider man issue's name was.. you know the one who got cloaned). Like water man, accept for the milk thing, he can transform his body into milk and he can also shoot milk from his hands (like Ha-do-ken...milky hadoken )  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ). While in milky form it drains a small amount from his supply of milk in his body (yep, he has a supply in him,  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ).<br>
<br>
When this resevoir is depleted he cannot use this power... until he gets more milk of course... which explains why he's always drinking milk.<br>
<br>
And to add a lil fun in it, he can also control the level of creaminess of the milk, the higher the creaminess, the higher level of milk drained aswell.<br>
